⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Settings & Configuration Module acts as the central administration and business configuration layer for the entire Jewellery ERP platform.

Every business rule, financial rule, operational rule, notification rule, and system behavior is controlled through this module.

Responsibilities:

* Business Configuration
* Branch Configuration
* Interest Configuration
* GST Configuration
* Notification Configuration
* Printer Configuration
* Backup & Restore
* Subscription Management
* Theme & Branding
* Number Series Management
* Master Data Management
* Application Preferences

⸻

