5. Core Business Rules

BR-SET-001

Only Owner can modify settings.

BR-SET-002

Configuration changes generate audit logs.

BR-SET-003

Historical transactions retain original settings.

BR-SET-004

Critical changes require confirmation.

BR-SET-005

Settings changes are versioned.

BR-SET-006

Backup before restore mandatory.

BR-SET-007

Deleted configurations remain archived.

BR-SET-008

All modules consume settings through configuration service.

